ASTRONOMY: Study of stars, planets, and the night sky

Category: Science
Base skill: 30% (+5%/level, cap 98%)

Knowledge of stars, planets, and celestial movement: navigating by
the night sky, keeping track of dates and seasons, and recognizing
when something in the sky is not behaving the way it should.

NOTES:
  No AetherMUD command currently rolls this skill directly. It is
  available for character concept and staff-adjudicated roleplay.

